item.description:
youtube-dl is a great tool to download youtube stuff.
Here is some helper script I used.
# download as mp4, playlist also function youtube-dl-mp4() { youtube-dl -f &#34;[height &lt;=? 720][tbr&gt;500]&#34; --yes-playlist $1 } # download as mp3 function youtube-dl-mp3() { youtube-dl -x --audio-format mp3 --add-metadata $1 } # download subtitle en function youtube-dl-sub() { youtube-dl --write-sub --sub-lang en --skip-download $1 }
